OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing to leave a cool evening with
OL,7,Flate sunny spells. Temperatures
OL,8,Frebounding slightly as cloud builds
OL,9,Fovernight, with rain arriving from the
OL,10,Fwest during the early hours of
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA wet morning as rain
OL,14,Fspreads across the region, locally
OL,15,Fheavy at times. Rain turning lighter
OL,16,Fand patchier in the afternoon, but
OL,17,Fremaining widely cloudy. Feeling muggy
OL,18,Fdespite being windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
