OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy and breezy on Friday with
OL,7,Fpatchy rain. Drier and warmer over the
OL,8,Fweekend, with winds also easing. Sunny
OL,9,Fspells emerging, but low cloud and fog
OL,10,Flingering along coasts.
